title: Drunk Girls Love Cellphones
description:
Written by Alene Latimer
Starring: Lisa Kleinman, Langan Kingsley, Kelly Hudson, Avery Monsen, Alene Latimer, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, Jon Marballi

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, March 4, 2013.

Filmed by Tom Levin, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
